snippet.title: Rocket Knight trailer (PS3, 360, PC)
snippet.description:
Seeing as how I'm an old fan of Konami's former mascot, I just HAD to put this one up.
The game is called Rocket Knight, and it'll be available on the Playstation Network, Xbox Live Arcade, and Steam.

I'll get back to MUGEN videos soon, but I'm just taking a whee little break right now.

Video from 1up.com
